content:
a time to be born,
and a time to die;
a time to plant,
and a time to pluck up that which is planted;

a time to kill,
and a time to heal;
a time to break down,
and a time to build up;

a time to weep,
and a time to laugh;
a time to mourn,
and a time to dance;

a time to cast away stones,
and a time to gather stones together;
a time to embrace,
and a time to refrain from embracing;

a time to seek,
and a time to lose;
a time to keep,
and a time to cast away;

a time to tear,
and a time to sew;
a time to keep silence,
and a time to speak;
